thread.title: CustomJohn Swan

author: CustomJohn Swan
title: CustomJohn Swan
text: My knew skiing goggle inserts worked very well with almost no fogging. I am very pleased with them. When I tried to look down to walk up the ski lodge stairs, the stairs looked closer and steeper than they were, but I think this will pass as my eyes grow accustom to them. Than you and I will share GogglesNMore to my other glasses wearing friends. John
